readme:
ZC Dark Syntax

ZC Dark is an alternate syntax theme that works best with One Dark UI in Atom. Should work with any language. ### Using ZC Dark: ![Example](https://i.imgur.com/UtCjgX4.png) ### Using One Dark Syntax (for comparison): ![Example](https://i.imgur.com/M4aEhkS.png?1) ### Installation 1. Head to your settings panel. 2. Click Install. 3. Search for zc-dark-syntax. 4. Click Install on the entry labeled zc-dark-syntax. 5. Go to themes and select it under syntax.
